milestones.description: Rick McCosker and Alan Turner's 182-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 176 between Fletcher and Dennis Amiss
Rick McCosker and Alan Turner's 182-run partnership is the highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 113 between Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad
Doug Walters and Greg Chappell's 117-run partnership is the highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 103 between Paul Sheahan and Greg Chappell
Tissera has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (28) in an innings in ODIs for SL, going past de Silva's 8
Tissera has become the top scorer for SL in ODIs with 66 runs, going past de Silva's 21
Alan Turner's 101 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for AUS), surpassing Ian Chappell's 86
Wettimuny's 53 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SL), surpassing de Silva's 21
Greg Chappell has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for AUS, going past Ian Chappell
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for SL, going past Fernando
Mevan Pieris has conceded the most runs in an innings (68) in ODIs for SL, going past de Silva's record of 33
Rick McCosker and Alan Turner's 182-run partnership is AUS's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 136 between Stackpole and Ian Chappell
Tennekoon and Tissera's 82-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 28 between Kaluperuma and de Silva
Rick McCosker and Alan Turner's 182-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 63 between Rick McCosker and Alan Turner
Doug Walters and Greg Chappell's 117-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 103 between Paul Sheahan and Greg Chappell
Fernando and Wettimuny's 30-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 5 between Fernando and Warnapura
Tennekoon and Tissera's 82-run partnership is SL's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between David Heyn and Warnapura
Tissera and Ranasinghe's 22-run partnership is SL's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 5 between Tissera and Warnapura
